Annotation Type Tab


  • public @interface Tab
    Defines a Tab in a Component dialog.

      • touchUINodeName

        public abstract String touchUINodeName
        Applicable to Touch-UI only Allows direct control over the name of the node generated for the Tab. This is useful in situations where you are supertyping a resource or you plan for your resource to be supertyped as it allows for the dialog structure to be shared by the inheriting components which is necessary for the resource merger mechanisms to act as expected. If unset the tab names will continue to default to a sanitized version of the title.
        Default:
        ""
